*Verovao* je u sopstvene sposobnosti. (He believed in his own abilities.)

On je *verovao* da će sve biti u redu. (He believed that everything would be alright.)

Ona je *verovala* da će ona biti uspešna. (She believed that she would be successful.)

Oni su *verovali* da će mogu da postignu svoj cilj. (They believed that they could achieve their goal.)

*Verovali* su da će oni uvek biti tu jedni za druge. (They believed that they would always be there for each other.)